verbose_text: New CARs were cloned and expressed from the pETDuet-1 plasmid in E. coli MG1655 RARE (DE3) as previously established in our lab.12, 14 This strain harbors specific knock outs that reduce its ability to reduce aromatic aldehydes further to their corresponding alcohols.25 DsCAR was well expressed, whereby approximately equal amounts were detected in soluble and insoluble fraction.
